Class FibonacciTask

  • java.lang.Object
    • api.Task<java.lang.Integer>
      • tasks.FibonacciTask
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class FibonacciTask
extends Task<java.lang.Integer>
    This class represents the unit of work involved in computing the Fibonacci sum of a given value. Each subtask computes the fibonacci sum of a value lesser than the original value and the results are composed to form the fibonacci of the original value.
